KULINDELEKE ukuthi avele namhlanje enkantolo umfundi wakwaGrade 11 osolwa ngokubulala umfana obefunda uGrade 1 esikoleni saseNorth West. Umfundi obulewe ugwazelwe esikoleni ngoLwesithathu ekuseni. Umnyango wezeMfundo kulesi sifundazwe uthe umsolwa ubecashe ethoyilethe lesikole kanti kusolwa ukuthi ulale kulo. Kubikwa ukuthi ubanjwe uthishanhloko wabe esebizelwa amaphoyisa. Kuthiwa umsolwa ubemazi umfundi obulewe kwazise wayethandana nodadewabo omdala abefunda naye esikoleni. Ungqongqoshe wezeMfundo kulesi sifundazwe uMnuz Jonas Sello Lehari kulindeleke ukuthi ahambele lesi sikole namhlanje ekuseni. Kwenzeka lesi sigameko nje nonyaka zilokhe zande njalo izehlo zokubulawa kwabafundi emagcekeni esikole. 